HEADWORD: Slumgum
<hw>Slum"gum`</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>The impure residue,
consisting of cocoons, propolis, etc., remaining after the wax is
extracted from honeycombs.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>Webster 1913 Suppl.</source>]</p>

